[I] Hardware Abstraction Layer

[T] HAL (Hardware Abstraction Layer) is a specification and an
[T] implementation of a hardware abstraction layer. It encompasses a
[T] shared library for use in applications, a daemon, a hotplug tool,
[T] command line tools, and a set of stock device info files. 

